title: North West Now Modeling and Designing Kimye's Upcoming Kid's Line
text:
North West Now Modeling and Designing Kimye's Upcoming Kid's Line 
Kim Kardashian made a very special Snapchat announcement last night… Most Popular By Alyssa Bailey Feb 1, 2017 North West, child prodigy , made her official foray into modeling and fashion design last night when she wore the very first pieces of the Kim Kardashian-Kanye West children's line on her mother's Snapchat. "See, daddy and mommy are doing a kid's line, and these are some of the pieces," Kardashian explained. "Northie picked out the colors and the fabric." A video posted by Kim Kardashian Snapchats (@kimksnapchats) on Jan 31, 2017 at 5:15pm PST Advertisement - Continue Reading Below A photo posted by Kim Kardashian Snapchats (@kimksnapchats) on Jan 31, 2017 at 5:14pm PST Most Popular North also rehearsed her moves for the line's first visual campaign: A video posted by Kim Kardashian Snapchats (@kimksnapchats) on Jan 31, 2017 at 5:11pm PST A video posted by Kim Kardashian Snapchats (@kimksnapchats) on Jan 31, 2017 at 5:09pm PST Advertisement - Continue Reading Below A video posted by Kim Kardashian Snapchats (@kimksnapchats) on Jan 31, 2017 at 5:07pm PST Over on Twitter, Kardashian got a little playful when she retweeted a fan's "RT fi you're getting pregnant in time for the Kim + Kanye kids line launch" post, with a bunch of emojis. 
— Kim Kardashian West (@KimKardashian) February 1, 2017 But before the internet could take it as a sign that Kardashian was expecting her third child, Kardashian shut the rumor down. Whether she's trying or exploring surrogacy is unclear for now. @KimKardashian are you saying you're pregnant Kim?? 
